fields.description:
When configuring an external Diff Tool the variable assignments for $LOCAL and $REMOTE are the other way round. If for example the following is configured:

Diff Command {{osascript}} with arguments:
{code}
-e "tell app \"System Events\" to display dialog \"LOCAL=$LOCAL REMOTE=$REMOTE\""
{code}

The following is displayed for a file test.properties with local changes:
{{LOCAL=/var/folders/zb/zjxy59t53514yy4zf1707rq40000gn/T//7R1nIp_test.properties REMOTE=test.properties}}
